name: Fonglets Marge Simpson
description:
Pretty good for just single pics of marge by herself. Works well with a most hentai models Anyhentai, Grapefruit, AOM, Kotos, AbyssOrange

Due to the significant difference in character art style does not play well with other characters. So getting reasonable intercourse is difficult but not impossible.

Inaccuracies.

Sometimes double pupils, no pupils or pupils facing in different directions. Easy to inpaint out or in though.

Hair is usually too short I believe because I attempted to train on hair up and hair down pictures which despite proper tagging doesn't recognize properly. (maybe try afro prompt which was what it was trained on)

Teeth are a little bit weird sometimes.
